---
// Call to Action section component
---

<section id="pricing" class="py-24 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-600 to-secondary-600 text-white">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="text-center">
      <!-- Main CTA -->
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl">
        开始您的创业想法管理之旅
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-6 text-lg text-primary-100 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        加入数千名创业者的行列，使用我们的平台系统化管理和评估您的创业想法。
        现在开始，完全免费。
      </p>
      
      <!-- CTA Buttons -->
      <div class="mt-10 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4">
        <a
          href="/dashboard"
          class="w-full sm:w-auto bg-white text-primary-600 hover:bg-primary-50 px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-semibold text-lg transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-lg hover:-translate-y-1 group"
        >
          立即免费开始
          <span class="inline-block ml-2 transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-1">→</span>
        </a>
        <a
          href="/demo"
          class="w-full sm:w-auto bg-transparent border-2 border-white text-white hover:bg-white hover:text-primary-600 px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-semibold text-lg transition-all duration-300 group"
        >
          观看演示
          <span class="inline-block ml-2 transition-transform group-hover:scale-110">▶</span>
        </a>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Features highlight -->
      <div class="mt-16 grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 bg-white/20 rounded-lg mx-auto mb-4 flex-shrink-0" style="width: 3rem; height: 3rem; max-width: 3rem; max-height: 3rem;">
            <div class="w-6 h-6 bg-green-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-sm">
              ✓
            </div>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">完全免费</h3>
          <p class="text-primary-100 text-sm">
            核心功能永久免费使用，无隐藏费用
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 bg-white/20 rounded-lg mx-auto mb-4 flex-shrink-0" style="width: 3rem; height: 3rem; max-width: 3rem; max-height: 3rem;">
            <div class="w-6 h-6 bg-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-primary-600 font-bold text-sm">
              👤
            </div>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">无需团队</h3>
          <p class="text-primary-100 text-sm">
            个人使用或团队协作，灵活适应您的需求
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 bg-white/20 rounded-lg mx-auto mb-4 flex-shrink-0" style="width: 3rem; height: 3rem; max-width: 3rem; max-height: 3rem;">
            <div class="w-6 h-6 bg-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-primary-600 font-bold text-sm">
              ⚡
            </div>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">即时设置</h3>
          <p class="text-primary-100 text-sm">
            30秒内完成设置，立即开始管理想法
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Social proof -->
      <div class="mt-16 pt-8 border-t border-white/20">
        <p class="text-primary-100 text-sm mb-6">
          已有 <span class="font-semibold text-white">1000+</span> 创业者在使用我们的平台
        </p>
        
        <!-- Testimonial -->
        <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          <blockquote class="text-lg italic text-primary-100">
            "这个平台彻底改变了我管理创业想法的方式。AI增强功能帮我发现了很多之前没有考虑到的市场机会。"
          </blockquote>
          <div class="mt-4 flex items-center justify-center">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-white/20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-3">
              <span class="text-sm font-semibold">张</span>
            </div>
            <div class="text-left">
              <div class="font-semibold text-white">张创业者</div>
              <div class="text-primary-200 text-sm">科技创业公司创始人</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Final CTA -->
      <div class="mt-12">
        <p class="text-primary-100 text-sm mb-4">
          准备好了吗？只需要一分钟就能开始
        </p>
        <a
          href="/dashboard"
          class="inline-flex items-center bg-white text-primary-600 hover:bg-primary-50 px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-medium transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-lg hover:-translate-y-1 group"
        >
          开始免费使用
          <span class="ml-2 transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-1">→</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
